defaultPreparing this submission has been an interesting exercise for BU, and we are extremely grateful to everyone who gave up their time to put forward comments and experiences. We strongly believe in the value of diversity and the p
defaultositive effect that it has on our ability to be creative and innovative. We also feel very strongly that it is completely unacceptable for anyone to feel harassed or subject to underlying prejudice. 
